{"tid":529487,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺譯名呢樣野好撚on9?","createTime":"2018-01-14T22:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T05:18:22.000Z","uid":13082,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"84b3f9a5732f7f0947d979d77cea94884b42c308","tid":529487,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:09:16.000Z","msg":"其實意譯都無問題，起碼都可以轉達到個意思<br />\n但音譯我覺得真係好多餘<br />\n格硬將個英文音譯做中文音，特別係中文係圖意既文字，每個字都有佢既意思，唔似字母<br />\n姐係音譯既過程背後仲可能扭曲埋人地個意思<br />\n例子：trump&mdash;&gt;川普<br />\n雖然個音最似，但都係同本身英文個音有差距<br />\n而且「川」同「普」令到個名譯做中文既時候多左其他印象，但其實本身英文冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：非文科，冇相關既知識，只係有呢個感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ea5c644b61331d9f4657cbd9dcf67cfb576e4d","tid":529487,"uid":164266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"84b3f9a5732f7f0947d979d77cea94884b42c308","tid":529487,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:09:16.000Z","msg":"其實意譯都無問題，起碼都可以轉達到個意思<br />\n但音譯我覺得真係好多餘<br />\n格硬將個英文音譯做中文音，特別係中文係圖意既文字，每個字都有佢既意思，唔似字母<br />\n姐係音譯既過程背後仲可能扭曲埋人地個意思<br />\n例子：trump&mdash;&gt;川普<br />\n雖然個音最似，但都係同本身英文個音有差距<br />\n而且「川」同「普」令到個名譯做中文既時候多左其他印象，但其實本身英文冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：非文科，冇相關既知識，只係有呢個感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:10:13.000Z","msg":"咁唔識英文既人點算"},{"pid":"1b8f7e75a6bdc0b777e94e96ee2bf9b2f03423c6","tid":529487,"uid":97240,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:12:38.000Z","msg":"trump 係侵"},{"pid":"4ebc4cdb3377ed6b8238e9edd9f80fac2c8dd1d0","tid":529487,"uid":39431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:17:27.000Z","msg":"殖民地時代留低既譯英國人名好優雅 ， 中文有意思又保留到一定程度英文原本個音<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160715/55362381\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160715%2F55362381&d=TkXmfuOGQkSNq9N2GwKPZRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=0da2aa36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160715%2F55362381&h=1af85e43\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20160715/55362381</a>"},{"pid":"f2c5a459d427fa59aab09c36335f2fca2376f5c4","tid":529487,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:38:00.000Z","msg":"吓....譯名名做乜要理會個字嘅意形<br />\n唔係話鳩用個同音字都得，但一定係用個最似嘅音先，再諗用咩字<br />\n唔通new york要譯做 新約克?<br />\n你覺得川普譯得差，因為係支那用左，唔係因為譯法問題。我覺得中文譯做特朗普係譯得仲差，反而叫當奴侵仲準，係譯得唔文雅"},{"pid":"49011534445cf6f8221eb6150357e4291445a920","tid":529487,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:44:16.000Z","msg":"咁 Trump 本身係咩意思？"},{"pid":"126a3177ac0d46038a7b5fa51be15b235a5cdae4","tid":529487,"uid":52590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:53:28.000Z","msg":"英文名點會冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地都有字源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ad4691f17048cc6d54ef69d990edf7baee0d94","tid":529487,"uid":97240,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T23:09:02.000Z","msg":"係而家d 中国人譯得on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f5a1e9ed859a14418e0b72f52ec457180aabf3","tid":529487,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T01:27:39.000Z","msg":"以前譯音之後有括返個原文，唔知幾時無左呢樣咁好既野"},{"pid":"9fd8e91c2a4254d828fc4161c6734bbf305c1ef4","tid":529487,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"126a3177ac0d46038a7b5fa51be15b235a5cdae4","tid":529487,"uid":52590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T22:53:28.000Z","msg":"英文名點會冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地都有字源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:06:36.000Z","msg":"可以查字源，但大部份人唔會知<br />\n姓 郭/趙/魏/曹/廖/韋 粒字點解？<br />\n姓嗰條友都未必知<br />\n即係冇意思"},{"pid":"5a766bd05da7d7261251e696cc8eaae268f353d9","tid":529487,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"音譯有意義嘅。<br />\n唔識外文嘅人咪要用到咯，韓國人都係架，一個韓國明星都好多種音譯名架，用字不同嘅種，但係我估都冇人會真係用韓文發個音出來去講佢掛？唔通下下都代指咩，啊嗰個呢，嗰個都教授啊，咁咪仲7，講嘢就係要直接啊嘛，音譯就係有咁嘅作用。<br />\n<br />\n至於你話譯得7唔7，就係另外一回事。有涉及一啲歷史問題嘅，前人（我指清朝民國嗰陣）譯開，舊版又寫開，你好難唔跟嘅啵。翻譯講求信達雅，但整咗個白話文出來之後呢，好多嘢都變曬，所以而家但求信達，雅我諗就真係冇點去追求嘅，而家應該唔會再有 翡冷翠 咁嘅譯名啦。"},{"pid":"92c0b3fc2abb7076bbbcbba33d61df498ba37e50","tid":529487,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"中台兩譯名先on9<br />\n例如obama<br />\n奧巴馬/歐巴馬<br />\n<br />\n非洲國家<br />\n塞拉利昂共和國/獅子山共和國"},{"pid":"d246177edef11dcabd4cf21857f017cb16667862","tid":529487,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"On9 唔理你咩科都唔應該On9 到以為英文在意思"},{"pid":"978015fdd3d9747c91f88d2fee4b4680f9fd8afa","tid":529487,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92c0b3fc2abb7076bbbcbba33d61df498ba37e50","tid":529487,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"中台兩譯名先on9<br />\n例如obama<br />\n奧巴馬/歐巴馬<br />\n<br />\n非洲國家<br />\n塞拉利昂共和國/獅子山共和國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"仲有宗教經典，基督新教/天主教<br />\n譯名都玩死人<br />\n<br />\nSt Peter  = 聖彼德 / 聖伯多祿<br />\nSt Paul = 聖保羅 / 聖保祿<br />\n馬太福音 = 瑪竇福音<br />\n約翰 = 若望<br />\nAmen =  阿門 / 阿孟"},{"pid":"cf7dd0cb619d30c2f0868bb41e7bdde003c4fa6c","tid":529487,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ntaxi譯的士扭曲曬原有意思，應該叫計程車<br />\nbus譯巴士又係，應該叫公共汽車"},{"pid":"0757adcf395d548115f518d29c2f5a7085891c5d","tid